            <title>[LU-18795] kernel update [RHEL 8.10 4.18.0-553.44.1.el8_10]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18795</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Security Fix(es):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: HID: core: zero-initialize the report buffer (CVE-2024-50302)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: ALSA: usb-audio: Fix potential out-of-bound accesses for Extigy and Mbox devices (CVE-2024-53197)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: scsi: megaraid_sas: Fix for a potential deadlock (CVE-2024-57807)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: pps: Fix a use-after-free (CVE-2024-57979)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


